data.description: ***Assumable VA Loan at 3.125% Payment is $1,038.43 per month***  Come see this move in ready, updated and well-maintained block home with large screened in Arizona room in the 55+ community of Sun Air Estates. 2022 -New kitchen cabinets, sink and countertops - fridge included, 2021-New roof and updated bathrooms, 2020- Interior painted, NO CARPET, 2022 -New luxury vinyl flooring. Washer and dryer included - large inside laundry, built in storage cabinets in the garage. Perfect Retirement or seasonal home. Recreation Center, Bocce Ball and Community Pool. Low annual HOA dues, $230 Annually. Next door to Sun City West, close to golfing, shopping, dining with easy access to freeways - Loop 101, I-10 and Grand Avenue/US 60.
